Wash, peel and chop @rhubarb{400%g}. 

Mix @flour{150%g} with @ground almonds{80%g}. Add @baking soda{1%tsp} and a pinch of @salt. 

Combine @sugar{100%g} with @butter{100%g} until soft and smooth, then add @eggs{2}.
Alternating add add the dry ingredients and @yogurt{100%g}.


Fill the dough in baking tin, top with rhubarb. Bake at 180&deg; for ~{45%min}.